I've started to decrypt the <<ReadNormalBandMemoryState send "ER010040BF;">>
part. My guess is that it is the same format as the first part of the
memory channels. It contains the last used vfo data for each band, it
gets written upon band change.

I have the suspicion that we got the mode values for LSB and USB
swapped. More test and I'll report back. 


